race.description: Spring Into Kilcoy Races & Pacing Oct/Nov Mdn Plate
race.comment: ENCRYPTED FEELING (2) put in an improved performance when runner-up at the latest effort and maps ideally for this from gate two. Capable of featuring prominently. SORT OF IN LOVE (11) is on debut but has been thereabouts in recent trials and this is not an overly strong affair. Any market confidence must be noted. VIPER ROOM (7) has hit the top-four in three of his past four starts and looks a must for the exotics players. MISHANI LETHAL (14) next in line.
